20074000.text: (The barong that Han Su-min talked about is over there)

20074001.text: (Ah?! The dispatched Young Teacher Barong was the <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Dong-Dong</> that I met at Lake Vandal!)

20074002.text: Iku-nyang! Eh? It's you! It's been a really long time! \nYour activity is also rumored to be spreading in <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Younggyowon</>!

20074003.text: (He said he heard the story and said he would help open the lei)

20074004.text: Really?! Go with me to that scary place and get rid of <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>boss</>!

20074006.text: In order to open the Ley, you have to operate a special device, and the <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>Boss</> is blocking it.

20074007.text: Come on, this explanation is enough!

20074008.text: Like is blocked here as well!

20074009.text: I have to grab the <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>boss</> and open the ley, which is rumored to be vicious.

20074011.text: Let's grab the head of the predators and open the ley.

20074012.text: This place is a dismal <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>Swamp of the Forsaken</>Nyanya.

20074013.text: Let's go mutate and kill the <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>The Lost Red Eye</>.

20074015.text: The boss of this place is <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>A tree that has lost its light</>. Come on, let's go.

20074016.text: I can't believe it, but it's said that there used to be a big village here.

20074017.text: Now, sadly, everything has been mutated…

20074018.text: There's a scary rumor that the Black Dawn is locking up kidnapped people here!

20074019.text: Let's get rid of the boss and open up a ley so we can <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>chukji</> here at any time.

20074020.text: This is the <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>Arsenal</>Danyang of the Black Dawn.

20074021.text: You have to defeat <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>Keeper Tanru</> guarding this arsenal before you can unlock the Ley.

20074022.text: This is the place where the energy of Takhoe is strongest in the Haeryong Mountains.

20074023.text: The goal is a terrifying <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>Kuma the gatekeeper</>Danyang! Let's go inside carefully!

20074024.text: It's like the Black Dawn guys are encamping up to such a high place...

20074025.text: Come on, let's go and kill <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>Boss</> and unlock the Leys!

20074026.text: The cemetery here is on a high place, so it didn't sink.

20074027.text: Then what the heck, even the <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>boss</> who should manage the cemetery has mutated...

20074028.text: This place is full of unbroken spirits. Aww, it's scary.

20074029.text: But I still have to do it! Let's put the dreadful <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>Busty Boss</> under the spot!

20074030.text: (You can see <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Float</> over there. Let's go and help unlock the Ley)

20074032.text: (I see <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Float</> over there. Let's go help)

20074034.text: (<textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Dong-Dong</> over there, it looks like the ley is also closed here)

20074036.text: (<textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Dong-Dong</> is waiting for you in advance. Let's go)

20074037.text: (I see <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Double</> over there. I think I need to open the lei here this time)

20074038.text: (There's a <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Float</> over there. Let's get closer)

20074039.text: (<textColor=[78:148:215:255]>floating</>waiting for me to open this ley)

20074040.text: (<textColor=[78:148:215:255]>I see a float</>. Let's go help unlock the ley)

20074041.text: (I'll have to clear these guys before I kill the <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>boss</>!)
